Step 1: Put the files in right place and include them

javascripts:
<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/prototype.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/raphael.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="/javascripts/image_operator.js"></script>

stylesheets:
<link type="text/css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen" href="/stylesheets/viewer.css">

Step2: initialize viewer

example:

<div id="viewer_menus"></div>
<div id="zoom_slider"></div>
<div id="image_viewer">
  <img src="/path/to/image/file" id="image" />
</div>

<script type="text/javascript">
    initImageViewer("image_viewer", "image", 950, 480);
</script>